 privilege join; "everything safe."**, **Movers lose old** role change isn't additive; privilege creep enemy., **Leavers deprovisioned promptly completely** departed-with-access gap loudest., **Reconcile accounts people** orphans/ghosts/shared risks., **keyring specs; operator executes** security-inversion., **Every change logged** unlogged access change finding. · f=IdP SSO maintain manual access matrix (person system access), reconciled cadence; discipline holds even without automation, labeled manual., Hack23 skill installed fall back general RBAC principles, labeled "no authoritative policy framework reasoning-based." Surface Hack23 skill adoption., Can't fully deprovision immediately (technical constraint) disable/isolate account first (fail-safe), complete deprovisioning promptly, log gap time-boxed exception (warden). · b:with Other Skills=**access-reviews** (sibling): periodic recertification catches what JML missed (creep, orphans). references Hack23 access-control-policy., **privileged-access-management** (sibling): privileged accounts get stricter JML., **Hack23 access-control-policy** (marketplace reference): policy framework skill wraps unaltered, `marketplace/` adopted-by-reference., **relay (AI Agents)**: relay owns AGENT identity/tool-grants; keyring owns HUMAN infra identity least-privilege doctrine, different subjects., **warden**: reconciliation flags deprovisioning gaps risks warden's register., **future People Culture**: authoritative joiner/leaver signal (HR) feeds keyring; keyring consumes it, doesn't HR.